blog.description:
Hi there!

I am Mr. DAPs, that guy with the hat that walks around Disneyland. I will mainly be posting some pictures that I have taken that I particularly like here but will occasionally post some other things.

You can read some of my other posts at any or all of the links below:

Blog: mrdaps.com
Website: dapsmagic.com
Twitter: twitter.com/mrdaps
Facebook: facebook.com/misterdaps

Please feel free to add me on any or all of the above links. I look forward to chatting with you and seeing you in the park!

Make it a GREAT day!

-Mr. DAPs

summary: Lego Star Wars: All-Stars to Debut on October 29
title: Lego Star Wars: All-Stars to Debut on October 29
body:
Lego Star Wars: All-Stars to Debut on October 29

Lego Star Wars: All-Stars will be debuting on October 29th for Star Wars fans everywhere. This newest series will debut on the Disney XD YouTube channel and also on DisneyNOW. This is a new adventure series that will span all eras of the Star Wars universe. The series is made up of eight shorts and four half-hour episodes. They will feature LEGO versions of favorite Star Warscharacters…

blog.name: mandowords
blog.title: Miit'alor
blog.description: I am a descriptivist linguist for the Mando'a language. I show what it can do, not what it MUST do. This is a place for discussion about Mando'a, and Mandalorian society and culture. Feel free to use the head cannons from this blog (or reblogged from others) in your RP or writing. All words and descriptions are taken from the mandoa.org Mandalorian Dictionary. Want to support this blog? Buy me a Kofi? OR buy some Mando'a themed items? Visit our Discord? Blog icon by Rina
